5
Living with one Move(1)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Beginner Life and Death Problem.
\par \b Black to play and live.
\par
\par \b0 There is a famous vital point in the corner.
\par It is the \cf1\b 1-2 point\cf0\b0 . However there are two 1-2 point.
\par
\par One of the 1-2 points usually solves any life and death problem which appears in the corner in 90% of the cases.
\par
\par Where is the vital point for living in this case?\lang1033\kerning2
\par }
