Dia. 01 Failure 1
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par How about expanding the eye-space with 1?
\par Sometimes it is good, but now it is a \cf1\b greedy\cf0\b0  move. White plays the vital point at 2 and captures Black immediately.
\par
\par Even if Black connects at 3, White destroys the eye with 4 and Black can't live anymore.
\par
\par
\par }
