Dia. 02 Failure 2
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After Black 1 if White would play elsewhere, Black could easily live. Of course White is not going to let that happen.
\par
\par White's hane at 2 is the vital point.
\par After Black 3, White plays the \cf1\b placement of the three space shape\cf0\b0  at 4 which kills Black.
\par
\par }
