Dia. 04 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \cf1\b Black 1 is the only way to live\cf0\b0 . This is also the 1-2 point.
\par
\par After White 2, Black lives easily with 3.
\par If White would play at 3 instead of 2, Black would live with many points by playing at 2.
\par }
